channel.description:
[center][img]http://i43.tinypic.com/4kzqq1.png[/img][/center]
SOURCE LINK: project insanity normal pi all dupes fixed on runeserver
[center]Our plans with server, we are going to have couple worlds BH,Pvp,skilling main world, and u will want to start off in the main world to level up to ur granted level u wish and kill boss for ur pvp armour you wish and than if ur a pvp type person u pick a world u wish to go to bh it will tele u to bounty hunter when u login if ur not there, for the pvp world it will tele you to varrock if your not there and these worlds will hope fully all run off the same char file to make it more fun hope to see u soon! working on website after clients all done we will work on server sided and get couple things done and than we will need 10 beta testers we will pick so post below if u wanna beta test we will make a list on the main thread.
Story Line
the reason we are going to make Mystic-Effect is because we want people to have fun and gain a really good eco server have people playing daily would be sick for us, See people teaming up for dungeoneering and Bosses having fun with there friends making new friends.[/center]
